Dialogs.Dialog: Hey... Have you ever seen a donut shop selling wagons?
My friend said that the last time I bought it and ate it, it was really delicious.
There are many other delicious donut shops, right?
That's right... I absolutely love the donuts! I was told.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ Do you like it? I am very curious…….
I'm also curious. However, the store seems to be mobile sales... I can't find it at all.
really? Thank you, let's eat together if found ♪
(Ah, is that a rumored donut shop?)
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲! I came to deliver the promised one.
Wow ♪ Did you remember it properly? I'm happy.
Choose the type you like, so eat whatever you like.
Really, don't hesitate to ask me ♪
● I tried to choose what I like ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲... How about?
……delicious! All right. You know my taste, ▼
It's a pleasant season....... I'm hungry.
What is it? …… Ah, yeah, my friend said he found a delicious crepe shop.
It seems that every year, the shop is opened with a wagon only during spring. It seems that they are selling while moving around the city.
Ah, I also want to eat the crepes at that store.
Then, why don't you look for ●?
(Ah, is that a rumored crepe shop?)
▲主人公＊▲. I was in a hurry because I heard that a crepe shop was found.
You see, that's a rumored crepe shop.
Wow, really. The shop according to my image!
● I can't help but smell this.
Fufu... Is that a dumpling rather than a flower?
Anyway, let's go buy it soon.
If you don't crispy, you'll get more and more full?
Somehow... I want to eat cold food.
Yeah... Ah! Speaking of cold things, I heard that a gelato shop is coming to this town recently... Do you know?
I don't know, where is it?
It's sold on a wagon, so you don't know when and where you are. That kind of thing makes me more interested.
Then, if you see it, I'll contact you. Let's eat together ♪
all right. ● I will contact you if you see it.
(Ah, is that a rumored gelato shop?)
▲主人公＊▲. Did you find the gelato shop?
is that so. You see, that store.
A shop that is more cute than I expected. It makes me happy.
I have to get nervous and not eat too much.
I only eat one more. But would you be happy if you could taste it a little too?
Before, I talked with my friends about the taste of autumn. But everyone is disjointed and I think there are many.
Yup. Hey, what do you remember when it comes to the taste of autumn?
● Ha... saury, matsutake mushrooms, persimmons, chestnuts...
Yes, that! I was associated with chestnuts.
Good, chestnuts. By the way, it seems that you are doing mobile sales of sweet chestnuts recently.
Oh, I've heard of it. But I don't know when and where I am.
Well, I wonder if I'll look for it...
(Ah, is that a rumored sweet chestnut shop?)
Yeah, I don't mind at all.
I had something I wanted to give to ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, so I brought it in a hurry.
The taste of autumn. I want to eat it together.
I'm glad you remembered me. I wonder if I should feed it as a reward... Fufu ▼
When I was a kid... Did you bonfire and have a roasted sweet potato baked?
Ah, maybe there was such a thing.
The baked sweet potato wrapped in foil was so hot that I almost got burned. But it was sweet and fragrant... it was delicious.
I haven't seen that kind of scenery lately... On the contrary, I may not have heard much of the roasted sweet potato shop...
Oh, if you ask me... I wonder if it's somewhere.
Are you really there? Ah …… I feel like eating roasted sweet potatoes.
● Also. Should I buy it next time I see it?
Then please ask me too? Fufu ♪
(Ah, is that a rumored roasted sweet potato shop?)
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, I bought the usual one.
It's a roasted sweet potato from a roasted sweet potato shop. here you are.
I wish I had the nostalgic taste of my childhood.
Then I have to check it.
Hey, do you believe in UFOs?
Well... I think UFOs can't be said to be nonexistent.
I see. So if I say I saw a UFO, can you believe me?
No. Actually, my friend saw it. Take a picture of that child. He says, "I've been coming a lot lately, so everyone can take pictures."
Hmm... But if you can really see it, you may want to see ● as well.
Me too. If you find one, let's report it.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, have you seen UFOs since then?
What a pity. Did you see a UFO?
Actually, that's right. Look, this is the proof photo.
Lie, really? …… No !? Something is in the picture!
That's why it's the UFO that ● saw.
great! Can I copy this? I have to show it to my friends!
Do you know that ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is Towassy?
Towassy? Um... that's right? A giant creature that is rumored to live in Lake Tohano.
What do you know after all? You recently learned about ●.
I think this is a rather famous story. Many people have witnessed it.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ do you believe that story?
Well, I want to believe that there is... When I think about why no one can take a definitive image... Hey?
If you bring a photo, I would believe it... Fufu ♪
Actually, I was able to take a great photo!
Fufu, I got excited. It's a really great photo, isn't it?
It's a big scoop! You see, do you know what this is?
Yes, Towassy! ●, I saw it with my own eyes!
Wow wow! After all, there was Twassy. I absolutely believe!
It's about time for an intermediate test.
It's about time for the final exam.
That's not the case, but are you setting goals and preparing to some extent? Why don't you set a goal too?
Aim for the top 10 in the grade
Aim for the top 100 in the grade
The mid-term test is getting closer and closer. Are you preparing properly?
The final exam is getting closer and closer. Are you preparing properly?
Hmm. Then, could you tell me what your goal is?
Aim for the top 10 in the grade
Aim for the top 100 in the grade
It's finally an intermediate test. Are you working hard to study for the test?
It's finally the final exam. Are you working hard to study for the test?
You will study better if you set goals properly. What if I declare it now?
Aim for the top 10 in the grade
Aim for the top 100 in the grade
Well, you don't have to get tired of it, right?
Oh, there are no two words for a man.
You say that you've taken the plunge...
It's not amazing. I will support you too ♪
I see. I am supporting you.
Don't be encouraged when you say that.
Well then, let's do our best for each other.
Well then, the goal has been set, so do your best.
Alright, let's do our best together.
All of today's tests are over. How was it?
Good work. Did you do well in today's test?
Thank you for your hard work. Did you get the results you need?
Yeah... I don't think it's bad.
The test will continue tomorrow. Let's do our best.
Let's do our best so that tomorrow's condition will not be worse than today.
Let's do our best tomorrow so that we can always do our best ♪
Anyway, it's all over. Thank you for your hard work.
Well, finally both of them will be released! Thank you for your hard work.
Thank you for your hard work for a week. You really tried hard? Good ▼
Announcement of test results... What's going on?
Wow! There is a name in 1st place!
It's amazing, I was impressed. Let's take a commemorative photo.
eh? Oh, that's right. Anyway, congratulations!
...... First place! It's not a dream !?
I can't believe it... I can't say that.
Yeah, I can't believe it myself.
Eh !? No way, I wouldn't get the first place...
Did you make a lot of effort? I tried!
I got it in the top 10!
Wow, congratulations! Did you do your best?
It's amazing to reach your goal.
I'm glad I've achieved my goal.
Oh, did you put it in the top 10? Congrats.
I did my best. Is it a higher goal next?
Alright! Clear the goal within 10th place!
I was enthusiastic about studying for this exam.
Kanojo also has a high nose. There was such a nice boyfriend ▼
Oh, I have to do this much.
Then, next time, I have to do my best to aim higher.
Within 100th place... I was in. It was good.
For the time being, congratulations on achieving your goal.
What are you aiming for next?
Achieving the goal... I was relieved.
Oh, I have a dumb face. Couldn't you afford it?
As expected... Is the first place useless...?
Was the goal a little too high?
However, it's never a waste to try to reach first place. Good luck again.
Was it a bit of a crazy goal?
After all, it may be better to gradually raise the goal...
As expected... Is the first place overstated...?
Well, everyone other than ● is doing their best.
Yeah. I like you who can think humbly like that ▼
It was a shame... I thought I wasn't in the 10th place.
I'm sorry I couldn't live up to my expectations...
Don't you apologize? I'm doing it for myself, not for me, right?
If you feel frustrated, I think you can achieve it next time.
Next time, I should do my best. It's cool to have a high goal...
Gee... Isn't it even within the 100th place?
It wasn't bad at all... I'm sure I can go this time.
That... wasn't it in the top 100?
Is it still lacking in training?
seriously……? Isn't it in the 100th place?
Ah... there are things like this.
I have to do some special training to recover in the next test.
It was hard, but it's all done. Thank you for your hard work.
Yeah, thank you very much for ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
Now you can date with a refreshing feeling ♪
Oh. Let's have a lot of fun!
When the exam is over, it's almost summer vacation. What do you spend
Of course, it's a date with ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲!
The exam is over, but this year is almost over, right? I have to make a plan for winter vacation early ♪
Yeah. I think I'll spend a lot of time together.
Hey, do you know these rumors?
It's a story called "Ghost of Tohano Castle"....
Ghosts... ghost stories or something like that?
so! Recently, I heard something like a moaning night at Tohano Castle...!
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲…… It looks fun. I like not only fiction horror but also such familiar stories.
n/a. Well, don't you hate it?
Hmm. Tohano Castle... I can go if I want to go...
It may be too early to get out, but... good hurry, let's go now!
I wonder if it's around here...
It's quite large... Would you like to walk a little?
Hey, did you speak anything now?
...... Would you like to walk a little? What?
...... Are you ready to go home?
Yeah... I feel like I'm feeling sick...
Oh hey hey. What happened to that story after that?
I was surprised because I heard a voice suddenly, but... I was still worried. Would you like to go again?
I heard a voice around here.
Well, I'm scared when I hear it, but... I'm not satisfied if I can't hear it...
(Actually, it's a silly story, and it's better to keep silent so you don't get disappointed.)
That's it. Hey, do you know
There is a Western-style building in this town, right? It's a rumor about that.
It seems that a mysterious ritual is held every night at the Western-style building!
It's a mystery because I don't know it. It sounds like you can hear an eerie sound.
I do not mind? Isn't it?
Here... there is a pretty atmosphere...
After all, do you want to stop?
All right. At this time... I think the ritual isn't done yet. At least just a clue...
I don't really understand what's inside...
Hmm... I wonder if you can put it in from the front.
I'm not sure if people live there...
...... What kind of sound is this?
It's a ritual! After all, a mysterious ritual...
Hey, maybe I'm a little scared...
Yeah... I'm sorry, I'm going out with you...
Hey... what happened to that story...
I was scared before, but I'm really worried.
Will you go out with me again?
...... Can you hear the sound of the ritual?
I wonder if I heard it wrong... I don't think that was the case...
(It's okay to disperse the material, but... I'll keep it silent because it's a big deal)
Yes, I saw it in the news, right?
What were you doing in the news?
I haven't seen it... Bigfoot is an unidentified animal.
That's it. The footprints of Bigfoot were found in the mountains.
Only footprints? Bigfoot itself has not been witnessed.
Isn't it some kind of mischief?
Is it a prank... But if you find it, you'll get a prize, right?
right? Hmmm, I wonder if it happens to appear in front of me.
After all, reality is like this.
As you said, it looks like someone's mischief.
Of course, there is no talk of prize money...
That's not the case... Maybe it's just free to think?
But isn't there such a good story? Sorry.
Hey, do you know this story?
Actually, it's the valley of Oku Tohano.
Oh, a ghost story in the city?
Right. The ghost of a beautiful and unfortunate woman who died leaving the world undeveloped!
A beautiful woman... reacts to that? Is it a ghost?
You talked about "ghosts in the valley" before.
Has there been any new information since then?
That's nothing. Was it just a rumor after all?
This is... an email from a ghost... I don't know.
It's a prank, but it's amazing.
No no. Even emails from other people.
(I thought about it. Well, it seems that it was interesting...)
Hey, did you go to the amusement park together the other day?
At that time, it seems that I lost something.
A small drawstring bag. I wish I had liked it.
I see... Did you deliver it to the amusement park?
why? It may have been delivered.
Well, a recent rumor is that a ghost in a costume is picking up lost items at an amusement park after the park is closed.
What's more, the lost items picked up by the ghost must be recovered directly... they will be cursed!
Is that so. I'm a little worried.
Hmmm, would you like to ask for it?
It was good. Please put it in.
Alright. Let's find it before it's too late!
I tried to find it all...
It's quite large... It's already time, what should I do?
Hey, the park is already closed. What are you doing.
No, I'm sorry to bother you. But... I was looking around as it was because it was troublesome to change clothes... Did it become a rumor?
You had better stop before you get angry. Then you guys should go home early.
...... I'm glad I found it properly.
Yeah, it was good. Besides, I didn't have to be cursed.
I've come... Hey, can you put it in?
I can't go on my own... Find a guard and ask.
Isn't it... Will you give up today?
It's not always picked up by ghosts. Ask at the information desk if it has been delivered.
Drawstring bag... It hasn't been delivered. I'm sorry.
No... Will you give up today?
